The Krait presents - Trance Harmonics Radio Top 10 August 2016, containing the standout tracks of the month in a 53 minute DJ Mix. Every month, this kind of a musical journey is designed by him and it is always pleasing to the aural synapses. He never ceases to amaze! He starts off with deep and mellifluous tunes and slowly develops the set towards energetic and peak time tunes. With this showcase mix, he depicts an emotive story to the listeners and brandishes an edge in his music. This is what picture perfect and a pure studio made DJ set looks like.
